Package: libargus-pep-dev
Section: libdevel
Architecture: any
Depends: libargus-pep2 (= ${binary:Version}), libcurl4-openssl-dev, ${misc:Depends}
Description: Argus PEP client library for C - Development Files
 The Argus PEP client API for C is a multi thread friendly client 
 library used to communicate with the Argus PEP Server. 
 It authorizes request and receives authorization response back from 
 Argus.
 This package contains the development files (headers and libraries).

